    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032010/extras/90ce272a21a311311f4cb4faaaab6794.webp?t=1769590337\" width=641 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>The Supper: New Blood</strong></i> is a hilarious, story-driven horror adventure game for fans of  dark humor, bizarre puzzles, and exquisite food!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stewie S. Appleton runs the remote Twin Sisters Motel in complete solitude. He has no family, no friends, and no hope for a better future. He has suffered all kinds of humiliation and abuse from a cruel world, but he’s had enough.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by his family’s culinary legacy, he will finally take justice into his own hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From Octavi Navarro (<i><strong>Thimbleweed Park</strong></i>, <i><strong>Photographs...</strong></i>) and Susanna Granell, creators of the critically acclaimed <i><strong>Midnight Scenes</strong> </i>series, <i><strong>The Librarian</strong></i>, and <i><strong>Unwelcome</strong></i>,<i> </i>comes this crazy horror adventure game for fans of the genre.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A guilty pleasure for the most exquisite palate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032010/extras/1664d11aa8cbe319b83a4083b0974fc2.avif?t=1769590337\" width=600 height=185 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032010/extras/d87ff925d4a829291b2bb3c65c5bcd04.webp?t=1769590337\" width=641 height=59 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Refreshingly weird and macabre point-and-click adventure game. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Stewie, a lonely soul who wants to make the world a better place... in his own way. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Stewie fetch ingredients, solve funny, bizarre puzzles, and cook a delicious menu. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigate your guests' dark secrets, and then...choose your next victim! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tasty, colorful pixel art!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eerie original soundtrack and sound effects that will make your skin crawl.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And don’t forget to pet Inferno! He’s an orange cat, you know what that means...  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready! The Twin Sisters Motel opens its doors for you!</p>",
